-- OGX Finds Oil in Block of Brazil’s Campos Basin, ANP Says
-- B y   A n d r e   S o l i a n i
-- 2012-02-12T14:07:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-12/ogx-finds-oil-in-block-of-brazil-s-campos-basin-anp-says.html
OGX Petroleo & Gas Participacoes SA,
the oil explorer controlled by Brazilian billionaire  Eike Batista , found traces of oil in an offshore well in the C-M-592
block of Brazil’s  Campos Basin .  The discovery in well 3OGX72RJS hasn’t yet been declared
commercially viable, according to a posting on the  website  of
Brazil’s National Petroleum Agency. OGX controls 100 percent of
the well.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andre Soliani in Brasilia at 
 asoliani@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Goodman at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 